title: U.S. scrutinizing Nvidia’s China-bound AI chips to ensure compliance
description:
The U.S. government is examining three artificial intelligence chips created by Nvidia Corp. for the Chinese market to determine if they violate recently enacted export controls, U.S. Secretary of Commerce Gina Raimondo told Bloomberg in a report on Dec. 11. Raimondo said her agency works closely with Nvidia and other chipmakers to ensure new products […]
